{"tid":1441254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大阪難波FreeHongKong 活動感想","createTime":"2019-08-10T15:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T16:50:11.000Z","uid":3464,"like":92,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"93b10a5ca7e9f1b5e4e1b4098385fe030e4828dd","tid":1441254,"uid":3464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:27:40.000Z","msg":"今日參加左一個由日本人發起既free HongKong活動<br />\n要主係收集大家對香港嘅打氣說話<br />\n主辦人都話今日收集到嘅memo紙都會寄返香港<br />\n今日寫紙嘅有好多不同國家嘅人士<br />\n有台灣、法國、有澳洲、有印度等等<br />\n甚至乎一啲了解現狀嘅中國人都好支持我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我想簡報一下今日自己嘅所見所聞<br />\n<br />\n其實本身我都好怕今日可能只有小貓三幾隻<br />\n但有好多好熱心嘅日本人經過發現有今日嘅活動<br />\n之後就留低參與同幫手由五點直到九點<br />\n一直都為香港叫口號同埋呼籲大家去寫紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為我自己本身係日本留學<br />\n所以有陣時只可以靠連登<br />\n或者係Telegram知道香港而家係點樣<br />\n但藉住今日嘅機會我可以聽到連登以外嘅想法<br />\n<br />\n好深刻記得有一位香港空姐<br />\n佢話佢自己本身係政治冷感<br />\n但係睇到好多新聞之後佢都覺得一定要出聲<br />\n所以我想講嘅係大家做嘅文宣<br />\n大家做鍵盤戰士其實係真係影響到人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">請大家唔好放棄做文宣！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日當然有啲中國人黎挑機啦<br />\n但係喺活動嘅尾聲<br />\n有一個中國人佢同我傾左好耐<br />\n差不多傾左一個鐘<br />\n佢好理性咁問我其實香港發生咗啲咩事<br />\n咁我都盡可能解釋比佢聽<br />\n<br />\n解釋咗乜嘢係送終條例<br />\n解釋咗點解香港人會討厭中國<br />\n解釋咗香港面對緊啲乜嘢嘅民生問題<br />\n<br />\n之後佢都話呢啲資訊係之前佢哋唔知道<br />\n<br />\n佢同我講 聽完你講之後我都會支持你地<br />\n但係我嘅身份真係唔可以多出聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道已經維持左差不多二個月<br />\n大家都會好攰 休息唔緊要<br />\n但堅持到底就是贏利<br />\n我地有好多人支持架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 時代革命！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/81Tirwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F81Tirwx.jpg&h=1af162a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67acf67afd7bee3e0fd6e86730aa4f328a442715","tid":1441254,"uid":3464,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:32:32.000Z","msg":"雖然冇咩實質用途<br />\n但我好想比大家知道香港人不孤單<br />\n好多人支持我地架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"904fc58f5c5561153ce36df3e1937053e0f7c235","tid":1441254,"uid":282622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:32:59.000Z","msg":"[Reddit 文宣］少女無故被捕 推上國際<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1440869\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1440869</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"e68215a4209161daa3018c6c27bb3ec0a5dc5b26","tid":1441254,"uid":3464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"904fc58f5c5561153ce36df3e1937053e0f7c235","tid":1441254,"uid":282622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:32:59.000Z","msg":"[Reddit 文宣］少女無故被捕 推上國際<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1440869\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1440869</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:34:00.000Z","msg":"我推你 你推我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41416b810f0747e7752cb918595763d45babf8bd","tid":1441254,"uid":6308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:34:37.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a2e9ef7b36388fdc0ce1ce949278e67ae9b40aac","tid":1441254,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:35:55.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1bb6ab53bbdbf29aa85ae51b147b49772c1a3d","tid":1441254,"uid":282622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e68215a4209161daa3018c6c27bb3ec0a5dc5b26","tid":1441254,"uid":3464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"904fc58f5c5561153ce36df3e1937053e0f7c235","tid":1441254,"uid":282622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:32:59.000Z","msg":"[Reddit 文宣］少女無故被捕 推上國際