me":"2019-08-10T15:39:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"424b43a7aedc1ec6fb59a3ce2a6d15dc86e2fe06","tid":1441254,"uid":282622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d8c942b896388f99776f6d9257b296fe9198dd","tid":1441254,"uid":3464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"424b43a7aedc1ec6fb59a3ce2a6d15dc86e2fe06","tid":1441254,"uid":282622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:43:48.000Z","msg":"多謝手足咁努力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3aad4c1b66ef7b9ac8e2c8db25bcbdb525f5bf","tid":1441254,"uid":282622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6caf6d80e820c4eb6a9b396820a8875f49ea66","tid":1441254,"uid":282622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:44:43.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8fff860ab868a93ba756df85293e9e09a31b6c7","tid":1441254,"uid":105773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:03:46.000Z","msg":"support"},{"pid":"6647950fdd1900d3b7359772542c8058564cfbf0","tid":1441254,"uid":3464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:17:46.000Z","msg":"打氣打氣<br />\n我知道有好多朋友其實已經好攰<br />\n我身邊有啲朋友都話<br />\n每一個星期六日都去平日又要返工身心都好疲累<br />\n但大家睇吓其實世界上好多人都支持我哋<br />\n我哋並唔係得自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431851e2d264bad9e4f814fa26f0fcbeb9fddb27","tid":1441254,"uid":52559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:19:09.000Z","msg":"Liberate Hong Kong好過free Hong Kong"},{"pid":"35253bade89581ee7dc9bb18c0b628af709d3fce","tid":1441254,"uid":114497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:20:03.000Z","msg":"請問普遍日本人知唔知道日本yahoo有大量五毛?<br />\n一有香港/大陸新聞就走去護主 仲要踩低日本人<br />\n希望佢哋意識到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e74784f867ec5a3aad2d9b4e4f2903294fd945","tid":1441254,"uid":263366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:20:35.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff208d5cf2e8f4a070142944101cddc81fc0f779","tid":1441254,"uid":239873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:22:09.000Z","msg":"勿忘初心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 徹底撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 撤回612至今所有暴動定性<br />\n3. 必不追究反送中抗爭者<br />\n4. 成立獨立委員會，徹查警方濫權濫暴及元朗暴力事件<br />\n5. 全面落實雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n大家要將焦點放番落五大訴求到！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434850</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jc4BasB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjc4BasB.jpg&h=bdd5af61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eZBgasC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeZBgasC.jpg&h=9bbbfb4f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QcvXEkX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQcvXEkX.jpg&h=75ef0b38&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8tQgUWw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8tQgUWw.jpg&h=86d694aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f98c468be165de40e4aaf44f00c2bead0e10a6df","tid":1441254,"uid":3464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"431851e2d264bad9e4f814fa26f0fcbeb9fddb27","tid":1441254,"uid":52559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:19:09.000Z","msg":"Liberate Hong Kong好過free Hong Kong"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:22:44.000Z","msg":"因為搞手叫個活動做action for hongkong <br />\n主要口號都係free hongkong <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58127b10423cf07034a640bfbca25c85d8727a1","tid":1441254,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:23:08.000Z","msg":"八月了，風狂雨暴，<br />\n但我希望香港仍能團結一致，戰至最後。<br />\n<br />\nCome whatever kind of weather."},{"pid":"8d8b7f25e7ef1c90b200756142a735ce9ee8ef20","tid":1441254,"uid":3464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35253bade89581ee7dc9bb18c0b628af709d3fce","tid":1441254,"uid":114497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:20:03.000Z","msg":"請問普遍日本人知唔知道日本yahoo有大量五毛?<br />\n一有香港/大陸新聞就走去護主 仲要踩低日本人<br />\n希望佢哋意識到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:24:42.000Z","msg":"應該咁講其實電視上嘅媒體有啲都係奶共<br />\n佢哋知道嘅資訊始終都唔係太全面<br />\n咁當然有5毛今日都有挑機<br />\n<br />\n只可以講唔好覺得日本人會知道所有嘅事情<br />\n但正正因為日本媒體唔多報道嘅情況之下<br />\n都有好多人支持我哋我哋就更加要努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}